    <diagram id="page-auth" name="2. Auth, MFA and Encryption">
        <mxGraphModel dx="948" dy="664" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1400" pageHeight="900" math="0" shadow="0">
            <root>
                <mxCell id="0"/>
                <mxCell id="1" parent="0"/>
                <mxCell id="p2_title" value="&lt;b&gt;2. Auth, MFA and Encryption&lt;/b&gt; — how the orchestrator authenticates and solves MFA" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=#fff8dc;fontSize=14;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="10" width="1320" height="40" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_ref_page1" value="&lt;b&gt;From Page 1 (Runtime Flow):&lt;/b&gt; Orchestrator Step 1 (Authenticate) uses Auth Layer. Steps 2 and 4 use Adapter Layer." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#999999;dashed=1;fontSize=11;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="65" width="1320" height="35" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_keys" value="&lt;b&gt;K. Encryption Keys&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;Sensitive columns are wrapped with a&#10;per-tenant data key (DEK), which is&#10;wrapped by a master key (KEK).&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Production (Web):&lt;/b&gt;&#10;- KEK lives in Azure Key Vault.&#10;- Backend fetches KEK at startup,&#10;  unwraps DEK, decrypts at use,&#10;  never persists plaintext.&#10;- KEK access is audit-logged.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Electron client:&lt;/b&gt;&#10;- Dev-only — no production keystore.&#10;- Local builds use a dev KEK&#10;  scoped to dev only." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="120" width="320" height="380" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_authlayer" value="&lt;b&gt;Auth Layer&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;A registry maps each auth_kind&#10;(e.g. password, api_key, ...)&#10;to its implementation.&#10;The orchestrator picks the right&#10;one at runtime.&#10;&#10;Reads credentials only via the&#10;data-encryption wrapper — see&#10;&lt;b&gt;K. Encryption Keys&lt;/b&gt;.&#10;Never sees plaintext from elsewhere.&#10;&#10;session_store handles carrier&#10;session cache and refresh.&#10;MFA challenges are handed off to&#10;&lt;b&gt;G. MFA Plugin Registry&lt;/b&gt;." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="400" y="120" width="300" height="380" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_adapters" value="&lt;b&gt;Adapter Layer&lt;/b&gt;&#10;(The only place Playwright lives)&#10;&#10;ONE generic adapter for every&#10;carrier — no per-carrier files.&#10;&#10;Reads CarrierConfig from the&#10;carriers table:&#10;- login_url&#10;- listing_selector_spec (JSON)&#10;- auth_kind, mfa_kind&#10;- hil_timeout_seconds&#10;&#10;Drives, for every carrier:&#10;- login form submission&#10;- MFA prompt detection&#10;- doc list scraping&#10;- PDF download link extraction&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Azure egress caveat&lt;/b&gt;: traffic&#10;exits via Azure IPs, carriers may&#10;block. See Page 3 Principles." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="740" y="120" width="300" height="380" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_mfa_parent" value="&lt;b&gt;G. MFA Plugin Registry&lt;/b&gt; — SOLE canonical MFA list (includes captcha-bypass resolver)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;fontSize=13;align=center;spacingTop=8;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="540" width="1320" height="320" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_bypass" value="&lt;b&gt;Auto-Solve Tier&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;Resolvers registered against mfa_kind:&#10;&#10;- totp_rfc6238 — generates the 6-digit&#10;  code from the stored seed.&#10;- captcha_bypass — captcha-bypass header&#10;  (carrier-issued token sent on the login&#10;  request; falls through to captcha_hil if&#10;  the carrier rejects it).&#10;&#10;Bypass tokens stored encrypted (see&#10;&lt;b&gt;K. Encryption Keys&lt;/b&gt;) and rotated per&#10;carrier policy." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="60" y="590" width="380" height="250" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_human" value="&lt;b&gt;Human-in-Loop Tier (HIL)&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;Resolvers registered against mfa_kind:&#10;- email_link — see polling spec&#10;- email_otp — prompt + paste&#10;- sms_otp — prompt + paste&#10;- captcha_hil — prompt with image&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;Flow:&lt;/b&gt; Worker captures challenge, writes runs.status=awaiting_mfa, emits prompt event, UI shows modal, user posts response, Worker resumes Playwright.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;email_link polling spec:&lt;/b&gt;&#10;- Keep the SAME Playwright session warm (carrier flips state only on redirect within that session).&#10;- Poll cookies every 2 s for the first 20 s, then every 5 s.&#10;- Memory about 200 MB per parked session, so Worker concurrency cap is mandatory.&#10;- Timeout = carriers.hil_timeout_seconds.&#10;- On timeout: emit doc_retrieval.failed (reason: mfa_timeout), tear down the session, free memory." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="470" y="590" width="870" height="250" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_e_auth_keys" value="unwrap DEK" style="endArrow=block;html=1;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;fontSize=10;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;fontStyle=2;strokeColor=#b85450;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" source="p2_authlayer" target="p2_keys" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_e_auth_bypass" value="&lt;b&gt;8a.&lt;/b&gt; MFA: Auto-solve (TOTP)" style="endArrow=block;html=1;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;fontSize=11;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;fontStyle=1;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" source="p2_authlayer" target="p2_bypass" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p2_e_bypass_human" value="if auto-solve unavailable" style="endArrow=block;html=1;strokeWidth=2;dashed=1;fontSize=10;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;fontStyle=2;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" source="p2_bypass" target="p2_human" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
            </root>
        </mxGraphModel>
    </diagram>
    <diagram id="page-infra" name="3. Infrastructure, Data &amp; Events">
        <mxGraphModel dx="948" dy="664" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1700" pageHeight="1200" math="0" shadow="0">
            <root>
                <mxCell id="0"/>
                <mxCell id="1" parent="0"/>
                <mxCell id="p3_title" value="&lt;b&gt;3. Infrastructure, Data &amp;amp; Events&lt;/b&gt; — what the runtime depends on" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=#fff8dc;fontSize=14;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="10" width="1620" height="40" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="mlops" value="&lt;b&gt;I. Build &amp;amp; deploy infrastructure&lt;/b&gt; — shared with platform (see CI/CD &amp;amp; Azure Infra diagrams)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff8dc;strokeColor=#999999;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;fontSize=13;align=center;spacingTop=8;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="70" width="1620" height="310" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="acr" value="&lt;b&gt;I1. Azure Container Registry&lt;/b&gt;&#10;neurapodacr.azurecr.io&#10;&#10;• Backend and Frontend images&#10;• Pulled by App Service&#10;• Per-env tag: dev / staging / production" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#999999;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="60" y="125" width="380" height="115" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="sonar" value="&lt;b&gt;I5. SonarQube — self-hosted, dev-only&lt;/b&gt;&#10;• Static code-quality scans on v1-dev only · non-blocking&#10;• Self-hosted on an Azure VM&#10;• NOT part of the runtime data plane — informational only" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#999999;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;dashed=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="60" y="255" width="780" height="105" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="envgates" value="&lt;b&gt;I6. Environment Gates&lt;/b&gt;&#10;• &lt;b&gt;dev&lt;/b&gt;: auto-deploy on push to v*-dev&#10;• &lt;b&gt;staging&lt;/b&gt;: auto-deploy on push to v*-staging&#10;• &lt;b&gt;production&lt;/b&gt;: MANUAL workflow_dispatch · deploy_to_production=true · branch v1 required&#10;• &lt;b&gt;production-approval&lt;/b&gt;: additional gate for DB migrations (reviewer step)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="860" y="255" width="780" height="105" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="eventflow" value="&lt;b&gt;H. Event &amp;amp; Notification Flow&lt;/b&gt; — events.py → notifications → Mailbox" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;fontSize=13;align=center;spacingTop=8;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="410" width="1620" height="170" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ef1" value="Agent Emits Events&#10;(events.py)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=12;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="80" y="460" width="180" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ef5" value="POST /api/v1/notifications&#10;(notifications.py)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=12;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="950" y="460" width="220" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ef6" value="Inbox / Today View&#10;(Mailbox → Page 1 Clients)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=12;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1280" y="460" width="220" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="data" value="&lt;b&gt;F. Self-hosted Supabase — data tables&lt;/b&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f4cccc;strokeColor=#b85450;verticalAlign=top;fontStyle=1;fontSize=13;align=center;spacingTop=8;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="610" width="1620" height="320" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="cconn" value="&lt;b&gt;carrier_connections&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;• carrier_id (FK → carriers)&#10;• username_encrypted, password_encrypted&#10;• &lt;b&gt;totp_secret_encrypted&lt;/b&gt; — service-account model, NOT user 2FA. KEK in Azure Key Vault, audit-logged. If 2FA non-bypassability is required, do NOT enable Carrier B.&#10;• session_token_encrypted, session_expires_at&#10;&#10;No mfa_method enum — discriminator lives on carriers.mfa_kind." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="60" y="660" width="380" height="250" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="carriers_tbl" value="&lt;b&gt;carriers&lt;/b&gt; (data-driven registry)&#10;• id, name, login_url, is_mock&#10;• listing_selector_spec (JSON)&#10;• auth_kind, mfa_kind&#10;• hil_timeout_seconds&#10;&#10;Adding a real carrier = INSERT row,&#10;no code change.&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;ams_targets&lt;/b&gt;&#10;• id, tenant_id, name, is_active&#10;• connector_kind, connector_config (encrypted)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="460" y="660" width="380" height="250" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="doc_enums" value="&lt;b&gt;doc_types&lt;/b&gt; (free strings on runs.doc_type)&#10;&#10;Canonical 8:&#10;• policy_renewal · cancellation&#10;• endorsement · memo · invoice&#10;• certificate · deck_page · loss_run&#10;&#10;&lt;b&gt;attach_to&lt;/b&gt; (enum on runs)&#10;&#10;Four values:&#10;policy / activity / accounts / unrouted" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="860" y="660" width="380" height="250" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="acl" value="&lt;b&gt;Access pattern&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;• Self-hosted Supabase stack on the Azure VM, fronted by Kong. Backend reaches Kong via Azure App Gateway.&#10;• No public Supabase endpoint. Service-role key synced into App Service per environment at deploy. DB migrations apply via SSH tunnel.&#10;• Row-level security enforced on every table by tenant_id (defense-in-depth).&#10;• Clients NEVER hold a service-role key. Browser only talks to the backend." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff8dc;strokeColor=#d6b656;dashed=1;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1260" y="660" width="380" height="250" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="principles" value="&lt;b&gt;Key Principles &amp;amp; Known Trade-offs&lt;/b&gt;&#10;&#10;✓  Async job model: Run Endpoint returns 202 + run_id; Worker does the work; UI subscribes to runs row for status.&#10;✓  NO HARDCODING: carriers, MFA kinds, AMS targets, doc types are DATA / plugin-registered.&#10;✓  ONE generic Playwright adapter for every carrier (Page 2: Adapter Layer).&#10;✓  Backend is the SOLE Supabase caller. Clients never hold a service-role key. Supabase self-hosted on Azure VM, reached via App Gateway; migrations via SSH tunnel.&#10;✓  Three Azure environments (dev / staging / production), each with its own App Service slot, ACR tag, and synced secrets. Production is MANUAL dispatch only.&#10;&#10;⚠  TOTP seed in DB = service-account automation, not user 2FA. Document this explicitly to security review.&#10;⚠  Backend Playwright runs from Azure egress IPs → carriers may rate-limit. No Desktop production fallback (Electron is dev-only).&#10;⚠  Captcha-bypass header is enabled in production; tokens encrypted at rest, fall through to captcha_hil on rejection.&#10;⚠  Worker job queue on Valkey (Redis-compatible), co-located with self-hosted Supabase on the Azure VM.&#10;⚠  SonarQube scans on v1-dev only (self-hosted, non-blocking, informational)." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#999999;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingTop=10;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="960" width="1620" height="220" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="e_ef15" value="notification" style="endArrow=block;html=1;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=10;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" source="ef1" target="ef5" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="e_ef56" style="endArrow=block;html=1;strokeWidth=2;fontColor=#000000;" parent="1" source="ef5" target="ef6" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
            </root>
        </mxGraphModel>
    </diagram>
</mxfile>